snippet.title: Ocean's Heart - Nintendo Switch Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Ocean’s Heart is an epic top-down action RPG in which you explore a beautiful archipelago as a young woman named Tilia. Take on contracts to fight monsters, descend deep into ancient dungeons, defeat menacing foes, and unravel the mystery of Ocean’s Heart.

Out February 10th on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/oceans-heart-switch/

#OceansHeart #NintendoSwitch #Nintendo

Follow Ocean's Heart on Twitter: https://twitter.com/OceansHeartgame
